➜地摊经济出圈：HR成进阶版“算命大师”
http://www.sohu.com/a/400974341_100187626	8208
<p class="ql-align-center">最近，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微博、知乎、朋友圈...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">突然被一个新词刷屏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>----地摊经济</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小文姐被各路漫威英雄的“地摊照”震撼到了...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（图源@青红造了白）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200610/72e3e84e7a5e4dbbba9c33adc2f9ec18.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">妮妮牌烤肉肯定不愁客源嘿嘿~</span></img></p>
